Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.65,0:00:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,【98堂 Yamete 出品】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.56,0:00:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我是裕一的導師, 我叫鈴原
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:00:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼慢才來?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.77,0:01:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,要我打幾通電話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.24,0:01:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我兒子被霸凌要怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,班上發生這種霸凌同學事件\N真是感到很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.18,0:01:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我並非要和家長談，我想和裕一直接談
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.32,0:01:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,家長不用知道嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.13,0:01:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,以為這樣就沒事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.27,0:01:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那什麼表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.14,0:01:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是上司叫你過來道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.41,0:01:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,偽善者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你不夠格，叫校長過來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:02:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,(被怪物家長強暴的新任導師)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,給我好好磕頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,再低一點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,想死啊, 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不想活了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.93,0:02:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,給我爬起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.81,0:02:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,又來幹什麼啊，老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,事情演變如此, 真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天不是以老師的身份過來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.56,0:03:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,而是以個人的身份來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,裕一的身體狀況如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.59,0:03:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,一直躺在床上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,都是我的疏失，沒有注意到裕一的情形
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他有在家提過這件事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他都沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.01,0:03:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,真是腦筋不行的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,欺凌他的同學聽說是富人家的小孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,老師，不要管了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,請你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天是抱著決心過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,裕一的身體沒有恢復健康之前，我就不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,裕一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,身體狀況怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,在學校廁所被毆打成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,太過分了，在廁所也打成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,醫生說恐怕會有後遺症
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起, 如果我多注意一點的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,就不會發生這種事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有沒有老師能為你做的?\N老師什麼都願意做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那老師你幫他擦下體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是說什麼都願意做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸，不要這樣\N你閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,連這做不到，剛才還在說什麼大話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,老師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.43,0:06:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,請讓我做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.48,0:07:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,老師，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,老師，有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道青春期的小孩感到最痛苦的是什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.45,0:07:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,睪丸內積滿的精液無法射出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:07:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸\N你閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.99,0:08:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他會變成這樣你也有責任
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子弄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣搓弄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.28,0:08:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,上下去動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.29,0:08:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,老師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你不會摸肉棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你該不會是處女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,還真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就交給你了，老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,還是處女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣子不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.45,0:10:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你唸書或許很行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,老師你欠缺基本生活常識啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼老師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,幹嘛，幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,老師剛剛做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,如果向學校告狀的話會被解雇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.75,0:10:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，請你住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我承受太多壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,要我向媒體傳播出去嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,還是現在就上傳網絡?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不要摸, 不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N最近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.17,0:11:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,散播出去你可就沒那麼輕鬆了\N住手，你是要幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.32,0:11:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,等等, 你到底要幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不要, 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不要, 不要, 夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,來人啊\N誰會來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.27,0:11:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他會變成這樣都是你的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.21,0:11:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,誰希望自己獨生子變成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.42,0:11:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.95,0:11:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不要摸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.36,0:11:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不要摸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.03,0:11:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.16,0:12:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,老師你自己決定用哪個地方來謝罪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,謝罪？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.38,0:12:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,比如用肉棒去插你的小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,還是要來舔我的肉棒?\N你自己選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那個照片散播出去給媒體，你也無所謂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.48,0:12:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我小孩會變成這樣都要怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.89,0:13:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,散佈出去也無所謂嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.16,0:13:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那算了\N不要，不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不要說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,來舔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.18,0:13:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好好配合就不會說出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.25,0:13:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,說出去好嗎? 想被解雇嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不要碰我, 請住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.74,0:13:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,來舔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴巴張開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,老師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.92,0:14:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,裕一沒有媽媽照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.99,0:14:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是很可憐的小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這根肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是要讓以後也會當母親的你，能瞭解那孩子的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,再來舔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,有那麼難受嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.69,0:17:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子舔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.24,0:18:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,老師第一次舔肉棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:18:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,有舔過肉棒嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,處女，第一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒味道如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.14,0:19:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好好配合會讓你很爽的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.28,0:19:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,來舔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴巴張開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我是在教你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我是在教導老師你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,來把嘴巴張開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.60,0:21:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,沒嘗過精液的味道對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.21,0:21:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,射給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.22,0:21:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.32,0:22:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,精液味道如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.05,0:22:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.52,0:22:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,【98堂 Yamete 瀟灑提取】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.27,0:22:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽，打掃完了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.22,0:23:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,還是有個女人在家清潔最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.17,0:23:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,請你出去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.17,0:23:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,給我繼續打掃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.78,0:23:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我最討厭這種女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.85,0:23:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.46,0:23:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我討厭你這種女人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.61,0:23:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.54,0:23:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.23,0:24:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.90,0:24:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.77,0:24:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.79,0:24:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，不要
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.27,0:24:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.48,0:25:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,會痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.19,0:25:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.66,0:25:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.59,0:25:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.11,0:26:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,處女的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.51,0:27:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你還真有模有樣
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.98,0:27:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這打扮還真適合老師你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.13,0:28:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.73,0:28:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,最不一樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.47,0:28:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,處女味道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.16,0:28:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.36,0:28:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,已經很濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.41,0:29:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你也很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.77,0:29:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.05,0:30:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.36,0:30:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,有被這樣搞過嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.84,0:31:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.71,0:31:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.65,0:31:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.13,0:31:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.53,0:31:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,硬起來了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.47,0:31:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不要, 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.47,0:31:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，不要
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.14,0:31:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣\N不要，不要
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.95,0:31:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了，不要
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.45,0:32:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,要插了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.05,0:32:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好緊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.21,0:32:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好緊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.96,0:34:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.25,0:34:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.87,0:34:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不要, 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.22,0:35:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.16,0:35:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.77,0:35:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.45,0:35:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.05,0:35:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不要摸, 不要摸
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.32,0:35:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N不喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.59,0:35:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼態度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.46,0:35:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,痛，會痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.67,0:35:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,會痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.94,0:36:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不要舔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.61,0:36:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.75,0:36:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.57,0:36:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.24,0:36:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,才不好
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.78,0:36:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.46,0:37:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.01,0:37:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.02,0:37:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你爽
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.91,0:37:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,處女的小穴會有這種反應啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.99,0:38:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,住手, 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.39,0:38:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,要搓弄嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.13,0:38:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.21,0:38:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，會痛
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.32,0:39:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.79,0:39:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,處女會濕成這樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.27,0:39:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,味道如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.20,0:39:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我也來嘗一下
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.75,0:39:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,來舔了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.89,0:39:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.46,0:40:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.67,0:40:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,味道不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.68,0:40:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,舌頭伸進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.57,0:41:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.53,0:41:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.93,0:41:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股挺高
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.07,0:41:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股挺高
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.17,0:42:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,頭給我放低
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.24,0:42:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.52,0:42:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.29,0:43:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好緊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.70,0:43:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.32,0:43:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,很開心對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.26,0:43:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.87,0:43:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,濕成這樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.89,0:44:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不要…不要
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.39,0:44:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要，我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.94,0:44:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,反抗什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.54,0:45:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不想幹老師了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.42,0:45:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道，你想要插了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.49,0:45:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要，我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.97,0:45:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,過來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.31,0:45:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，不要
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.78,0:45:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好難受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.65,0:45:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,住手，住手，不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.48,0:46:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好緊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.71,0:46:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,看插入地方
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.60,0:47:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒插得很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.50,0:48:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股挺高
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.91,0:48:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,把屁股挺高
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.94,0:54:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,來舔一下肉棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.74,0:54:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴巴張開含進去
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.76,0:55:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不要離開
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.47,0:56:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.48,0:57:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.29,0:58:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.44,1:00:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.45,1:00:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,射裡面喔
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.25,1:00:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,射裡面很開心吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.92,1:00:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.34,1:00:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.30,1:00:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.43,1:00:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,射很多在裡面喔
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.77,1:01:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.91,1:01:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了\N住手
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.39,1:02:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你給裕一看你穿圍裙啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.53,1:02:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不覺得害羞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.00,1:02:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他沒有醒來
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.82,1:02:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這，都要怪你
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.49,1:03:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你向警察報案你就完了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.03,1:03:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,被那些混蛋毆打成這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.23,1:03:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得心安嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.51,1:03:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會向警察報案
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.71,1:03:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我回去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.85,1:03:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我無法相信你
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.59,1:03:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,像我這樣的沒錢的家長，就要受這種苦嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.73,1:03:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你當什麼教師啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.40,1:03:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,如果裕一好不了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.87,1:03:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,像你們這種老師能感受我們的痛苦嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.95,1:04:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒完耶
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.55,1:04:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,穿上這個
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.09,1:04:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,以老師及個人身份
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.69,1:04:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,以負責任的老師身份 給我去向裕一謝罪吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.37,1:04:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,【天鵝肉某大佬 出品】
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.32,1:04:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.59,1:04:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.06,1:04:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你是因為這女人的關係才變這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.80,1:04:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,來道歉
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.87,1:04:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.54,1:05:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不要太過分
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.75,1:05:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,裕一變成這個樣子喔
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.62,1:05:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,住手\N還沒完耶
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.02,1:05:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這女人的道歉像糞便一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.16,1:05:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,老師啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.50,1:05:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你跨坐在上面，給他著小穴吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.04,1:05:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧\N不要，不要
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.37,1:05:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.79,1:05:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,手給我放開
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.14,1:06:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.14,1:06:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,老師，說吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.81,1:06:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.61,1:06:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.49,1:06:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,在他面前自慰吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.02,1:06:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,自慰吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.76,1:06:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,捨棄自尊才算是真正的謝罪
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.63,1:06:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,自慰吧，不知道怎麼做嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.04,1:06:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會，不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.11,1:06:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子弄啦
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.52,1:06:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好好弄給他看
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.65,1:06:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.59,1:06:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣子, 知道了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.59,1:06:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,自己弄吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.35,1:07:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸不要那樣
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.96,1:07:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,老師正在道歉，你仔細聽
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.76,1:07:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,謝罪吧! 手去動吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.58,1:07:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.31,1:07:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.25,1:07:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,腳張開來
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.79,1:07:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了吧.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.86,1:08:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.82,1:08:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,發出聲音道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.65,1:09:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,處女這麼會噴淫水啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.19,1:09:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.86,1:09:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這孩子心靈受的創傷，可能一輩子都不會消失喔
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.27,1:09:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,去跨坐他上面
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.54,1:09:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你有聽到她道歉什麼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.48,1:09:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.62,1:09:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,老師過來吧\N不要
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.76,1:09:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸, 住手
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.43,1:09:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.76,1:09:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,去騎上去\N爸爸，住手啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.17,1:09:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,老師啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.57,1:09:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,紿我放進去
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.64,1:09:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.44,1:10:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼不要啊！老師
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.26,1:10:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不要, 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.00,1:10:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,裕一，這種道歉如何?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.74,1:10:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得不錯
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.88,1:10:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣我可以向班上同學炫耀
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.01,1:10:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.22,1:10:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,現在開始由你自己玩吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.82,1:10:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,要像這樣子動
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.56,1:10:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.92,1:11:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，不要
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.23,1:12:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽啊，老師
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.32,1:12:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.18,1:12:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,老師啊
