Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.37,1:15:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不要, 不要
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.67,1:15:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.41,1:16:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.16,1:16:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,老師，好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.70,1:19:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,老師，好爽啊
